</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">]-[</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">토익</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">TEST]-[</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">평가결과</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">/</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">피드백</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">]</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">2. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">졸업 외국어패스 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">nDRIMS </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">확인</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">  - </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">확인 가능일</span></span>: <span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">시험일 기준 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">7</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">일 경과일</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">주말</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">, </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">휴일 제외</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">) 16</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">시 이후</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">  - </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">확인 방법</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">: nDRIMS </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">로그인</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">교육센터</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">영어</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">pass</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">제성적조회</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:none;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">■ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">문의</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">:</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">다르마칼리지 학사운영실 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">(02-2260-3468, 3474)</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-autospace:none;font-weight:bold;font-size:17.0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;word-break:keep-all;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:나눔고딕;\">다 르 마 칼 리 지</span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\"> </div>",
    "본문": "2026\n년\n5\n월\n26\n일\n(\n화\n)\n모의영어 시험 고사장을 아래와 같이 안내합니다\n.\n시험종류\n수험번호\n고사장\n모의토익\n1 ~ 74\n혜화관\n3\n층 미래융합세미나실\n※\n자리 배치는 당일 현장 감독관이 안내할 예정입니다\n.\n■\n신청 및 응시료 납부 안내\n1.\n신청 기간\n: 2026.05.18.(\n월\n) 10:00\n–\n16:00\n-\n기한 엄수\n.\n세부 사항 아래 게시글 필히 참고\n동국대학교\n-\n대학안내\n-\n공지사항\n-\n학사공지\n(\n기타\n) (dongguk.edu)\n2\n.\n수납 기간\n: 2026.05.19.(\n화\n) 10:00 - 16:00\n■\n준비물\n:\n신분증\n(\n주민등록증\n,\n운전면허증\n,\n여권\n,\n카드학생증\n),\n컴퓨터용 사인펜\n(\n연필불가\n), (\n필요시\n)\n수정테이프\n※\n모바일 신분증은 불가하며 신분증 미소지자는 시험응시 불가합니다\n.\n■\n시험시간 안내\n1.\n모의토익\n: 14:00 - 16:00\n-\n강화된 신분증 검사로 인해\n13\n시\n45\n분까지 입실 바랍니다\n.\n- Listening\n시험 관계로\n13\n시\n55\n부터 고사장 출입이 제한됩니다\n.\n■\n시험 결과 확인\n1.\n성적 확인 방법\n-\n확인 가능일\n:\n시험일 기준 약\n4\n일 경과\n(\n주말\n,\n휴일 제외\n) 16\n시 이후\n-\n사이트\n(www.testclinic.com)\n에 로그인\n- [\n마이페이지\n]-[\n시험응시\n/\n결과 확인\n]-[\n토익\nTEST]-[\n평가결과\n/\n피드백\n]\n2.\n졸업 외국어패스\nnDRIMS\n확인\n-\n확인 가능일\n:\n시험일 기준\n7\n일 경과일\n(\n주말\n,\n휴일 제외\n) 16\n시 이후\n-\n확인 방법\n: nDRIMS\n로그인\n-\n교육센터\n-\n영어\npass\n제성적조회\n■\n문의\n:\n다르마칼리지 학사운영실\n(02-2260-3468, 3474)\n다 르 마 칼 리 지",
